Waxaa jirta laba hab oo loo xisaabo Cufka 

Xeerka labaad ee Niyuutan (''inertial mass'')haddii isku darka xooga ku faln walax aanu le’ekeyn eber, walaxdu waxa ay yeelanaysaa karaar saamigal quman ku ah laxaadka iskudarka xooga iyo jihaddiisa. Walaxda ''m'' awooda ''F'',Karaarta ''a'' Waxa ay kusiineysaa '''F'''/''m''. Waa halbeeg

<math>F(N)=m(kg)* a(m/s^2))</math>

:<math> F = G\,\frac{m_1 m_2}{r^2} \, ,</math>

Cuf is jiidadka (active gravitational mass) Walax ''m''<sub>1</sub> haddii meel la dhigo  Fogaan  u jirta  ''r'' walax kale ee cuf keedu yahay 'm''<sub>2</sub> walaxdi hore saamayn ay ku yeelanaysaa ''F' waa soo jiidanaysaa  sidaan ayaana tusaale u ah 

:<math> F = G\,\frac{m_1 m_2}{r^2} \, ,</math>

''G'' Waa ma doorsoome cuf is jiidadka guud waxa ayna udhigantaa  6.67*10<sup>−11</sup> kg<sup>−1</sup>.m<sup>3</sup>.s<sup>−2</sup>.





